.TH VIDMOD-CHAIN 1
.SH NAME
vidmod-chain \- run multiple vidmod plugins in sequence
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B vidmod chain
<command> [options] -- <command> [options] -- <input> <output>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Run two or more chainable vidmod plugins, passing temporary output from each
stage to the next stage.
